chrome off a trailer hitch.

05:26.873 --> 05:28.841
<i>It's a Modigliani exhibit.</i>

05:28.875 --> 05:30.327
I don't know which I find
harder to believe...

05:30.328 --> 05:31.778
that there's a Modigliani

05:31.813 --> 05:34.916
<i>in Harrisburg or that you got
boxed in a State Museum.</i>

05:34.951 --> 05:37.119
There was no box
in the schematics, Job.

05:37.153 --> 05:39.890
Well, not in the ones
you were looking at, baby.

05:39.924 --> 05:42.694
Oh, look, the alarm's
got a dialer.

05:42.728 --> 05:43.996
- State police are responding.
ETA... six minutes.

05:45.297 --> 05:47.366
I'm telling you,
you should ask her out.

05:47.401 --> 05:50.770
Job, I can barely hear you.
Can you turn this shit off?

05:52.374 --> 05:53.908
- <i>Is it off?</i>
- Yeah.

05:53.942 --> 05:55.443
Then I'm in there with you.

05:55.478 --> 05:57.112
<i>And I'm gonna get you out.</i>

05:57.146 --> 05:58.847
Okay. Is there
a manual release?

05:58.882 --> 06:01.951
<i>Not one that you can reach</i>
<i>without a blowtorch.</i>

06:01.986 --> 06:04.388
What's behind these walls?

06:04.422 --> 06:06.857
Solid stone. Someone knew
what they were doing.

06:28.418 --> 06:30.019
Hold on a second.

06:32.122 --> 06:33.823
- Hello?
<i>- Oh.</i>

06:33.858 --> 06:36.526
I figured I'd get
your voice mail.

06:36.561 --> 06:40.298
- I keep odd hours.
- <i>We need to talk.</i>

06:40.332 --> 06:42.134
Now is not really
an ideal time.

06:42.168 --> 06:44.169
Really? Well, it's the
middle of the night

06:44.203 --> 06:45.939
and I'm sneaking out
to my backyard

06:45.973 --> 06:48.141
because I haven't slept a single
night since you showed up.

06:48.175 --> 06:50.544
<i>You're putting me</i>
<i>and my family at risk.</i>

06:50.578 --> 06:51.945
Hold on.

06:51.980 --> 06:55.984
- <i>Job.</i>
- I know you did not just take a call

06:56.018 --> 06:57.953
<i>while I'm trying to save</i>
<i>your pasty, dumb ass.</i>

06:57.988 --> 06:59.455
Where are the cops, Job?

06:59.489 --> 07:00.923
Three minutes away.

07:00.958 --> 07:02.893
I am looking for an override.

07:02.927 --> 07:05.929
<i>Look harder!</i>

07:05.964 --> 07:09.434
Hey, Mama, you suck
any dick yet tonight?

07:09.468 --> 07:11.237
Yeah, like...
like maybe your own?

07:11.271 --> 07:13.038
Well, yeah, yeah.

07:13.073 --> 07:15.943
Wait, do you ever get bored
and tit-fuck yourself?

07:15.977 --> 07:18.312
<i>Ooh, she's gettin' pissy.</i>

07:18.346 --> 07:21.516
<i>- Oh, yeah.</i>
<i>- I think she's upset.</i>

07:21.550 --> 07:24.620
- I'll be right back.
<i>- What?</i>

07:24.654 --> 07:26.455
Job!

07:28.559 --> 07:30.059
Oh, we pissed him off.

07:30.094 --> 07:32.029
<i>Oh, yeah, we did piss her off.</i>

07:32.063 --> 07:33.864
I think she likes you.

07:33.899 --> 07:35.600
Hey, sweetie.

07:38.905 --> 07:41.875
Sit your bitch-asses down.

07:44.280 --> 07:48.150
Now I am going
back to my table.

07:48.184 --> 07:51.354
And the next one of you
that gets up out of this booth

07:51.388 --> 07:52.890
is gonna be pissing
sitting down

07:52.924 --> 07:55.860
for the rest of his life.

07:57.864 --> 07:59.582
- It's Zack's Diner, just
off the interstate...

07:59.583 --> 08:01.301
- Oh, sure, narc on a sister.

08:01.336 --> 08:03.337
She... I mean, he has a knife.

08:03.371 --> 08:04.772
<i>Job!</i>

08:04.806 --> 08:06.408
<i>Now we both on the clock.</i>

08:06.442 --> 08:08.476
Yeah, I'll be right back.

08:08.511 --> 08:09.945
<i>Ana.</i>

08:09.980 --> 08:11.713
- It's Carrie.
- <i>Listen,</i>

08:11.748 --> 08:13.115
we're gonna have to talk
some other time.

08:13.149 --> 08:14.885
No, I don't wanna have
another conversation with you.

08:14.919 --> 08:16.954
You need to stop this
for both of our sakes.

08:16.988 --> 08:18.356
Hold on.

08:18.391 --> 08:20.592
<i>Job, I need this door open now!</i>

08:20.626 --> 08:23.563
Job? You're talking to Job?

08:23.597 --> 08:25.231
Jesus Christ, you're on a take?

08:25.266 --> 08:26.734
Listen, I'm in a jam.

08:26.768 --> 08:29.503
You're on a take. Oh, my God.

08:29.537 --> 08:32.039
